#September 5, 2023

1. To check positive or negative number
GET number
IF number is greater than zero
PRINT “Positive”
ELSE
PRINT “Negative”
ENDIF
2. To check odd or even number
GET number
IF number is divisible by 2 with no remainder
PRINT “Even”
ELSE
PRINT “Odd”
ENDIF
3. To check greatest of three numbers
READ a, b, and c
IF a is greater than b and a is greater than c
PRINT “a is greatest”
IF b is greater than a and b is greater than c
PRINT “b is greatest”
IF c is greater than a and c is greater than b
PRINT “c is greatest”
ENDIF
